@wp.kernel
def rand_expr_muxmbl(data: wp.array(dtype=float)):
    tid = wp.tid()
    v0 = data[tid]
    v1 = 0.0
    v2 = 1.0
    tmp = 0.0
    v0 = ((wp.abs(tmp + 0.49) / wp.exp(v1 + 0.29)) - ((tmp + 0.54 * tmp + 0.18) + v2))
    v0 = (wp.exp((tmp + 0.44 / tmp + 0.03)) + wp.exp((tmp + 0.52 * v1 + 0.72)))
    v0 = v1
    v2 = (wp.exp((v1 + 0.35 / v2 + 0.91)) + wp.cos(wp.cos(v2 + 0.02)))
    v2 = ((v0 + (tmp + 0.34 * v1 + 0.95)) + 0.86)
    tmp = (v1 * 0.05)
    tmp = (wp.exp(0.85) - tmp)
    tmp = wp.exp((v2 + wp.exp(v1 + 0.25)))
    data[tid] = v0
